---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Return Policy">
  <section class="section-padding">
    <div class="container legal-content">
      <h1>Return & Exchange Policy</h1>
      <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: December 2025</p>

      <section>
        <h2>1. Returns</h2>
        <p>At Charming Choices, we want you to be completely satisfied with your purchase. If you are not happy with your item, you may return it within <strong>7 days</strong> of purchase or delivery, provided the item is in its original condition and packaging.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>2. Non-Returnable Items</h2>
        <p>For hygiene and safety reasons, the following items cannot be returned:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Used kitchenware or containers</li>
          <li>Opened electronics or items without original seals</li>
          <li>Personalized or customized gifts</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>3. Exchanges</h2>
        <p>We only replace items if they are defective or damaged upon arrival. If you need to exchange it for the same item, please contact us on WhatsApp (+1 868-467-8700) immediately with a photo of the defect.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>4. Refunds</h2>
        <p>Refunds are processed via Bank Transfer or Store Credit. Please allow 3-5 business days for bank transfers to be completed after the return is accepted.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>5. Store Pickup Returns</h2>
        <p>Items purchased via Store Pickup must be returned to our Chaguanas location for inspection.</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .last-updated {
    color: var(--text-light);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
  }

  p, li {
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    list-style-type: disc;
  }
</style>
